{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">PRESENTATION</h2><br>War is raging. The entire kingdom is about to collapse, as the mysterious vampire Chronus restlessly orders his troops to attack rebels and survivors over and over.<br><br>Valerie's future husband and paladin Martin left to fight the oppressor, but never came back. As her friends Lena and Sabrina struggle to comfort her, Valerie's mind is obsessed by no other than ONE thing: challenge the impossible, and go after her true love.<br><br>She doesn't know it yet, but her personal quest will impact the entire world!<br>As she befriends new companions along the way, the young lady and her two childhood friends, strangers to the battlefield at first, learn to fight, improve their strength, and eventually become leaders of the rebellion!<br><br>With its great production values, beautiful art and epic fantasy quest, Burning Faith is a Tactical RPG in the classic style of Feda the Emblem of Justice and Shining Force, that will satisfy the itch of T-RPG and RPG fans alike.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">FEATURES</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>13 playable characters with different profiles, strengths and weaknesses<br></li><li>28 exciting and tactical battles of increasing difficulty<br></li><li>About 20 hours of strategic and immersive gameplay<br></li><li>A New Game+ to replay the game with an extra character<br></li><li>Skills that evolve to Level 2 and 3 depending on use: choose which skills to favor in battle, resulting in unlimited combinations, strategies and ways of playing<br></li><li>Pure tactics and strategy: the troops, both allies and enemies alike, never do a critical and their damage are estimated before an action is decided, plus only a few selected enemies can evade, resulting in no miss most of the times<br></li><li>Adjustable Battle Animations Speed: 4 different levels for maximum enjoyment!<br></li><li>Mouse Control<br></li><li>Great Replay Value! While the main quest lasts about 20 hours, you may want to replay this game over and over to refine your strategy and/or discover new ways of playing, not to mention New Game+</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">HEROES</h2><br>The <strong>local heroes</strong>...<br>Valerie the musketeer, Sabrina the Lumberjane, Lena the Archer, Lukas the Warrior...<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1798150/extras/bf1.png?t=1730792345\" /><br><br>The <strong>professionals</strong>...<br>Josephine the Vicar, Slash the Thief, Evelyn the Diplomat, Guinevere the Witch...<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1798150/extras/bf2.png?t=1730792345\" /><br><br>And <strong>more????</strong>...<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1798150/extras/bf3.png?t=1730792345\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">PLAY MORE AWESOME GAMES</h2><br><br><br><br><br>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Forest Encounter","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1798150/cb85cc3c8df4708be8d3813339b924ef17ba95fb.jpg"},{"name":"War Base","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1798150/232390b443d8e274a11e337b8a9416015bbb4dda.jpg"},{"name":"River Mouth","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1798150/382233fef475f6df484d576123dacbf15c75d69c.jpg"},{"name":"Prison of Narjaris","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1798150/fdbc648035b37de00450f7026508da0c41f61b13.jpg"},{"name":"Crime Pass","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1798150/b1539ae425002ed4f85fe0393a0818940b3a5acd.jpg"},{"name":"Kharys Crisis","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1798150/3d375814f553813e84385654db28d0aef3b988c6.jpg"},{"name":"Old Kharysian Mine","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcomm